Usage:

// Instantiate
var image = new noise();

// Generate Random Noise Pattern
image.generate();

// Add the DOM Element to your Document
document.body.appendChild(image.domElement);

// If you have a RequestAnimFrame loop you can use noise.generate() to create a new pattern. 
MainLoop() {
  image.generate();
  requestAnimFrame(MainLoop);
}

...etc

Optional arguments for instantiation are: width, height, opacity, monochrome/color, size (not implemented).

Default values are Width/Height: 200px, Opacity: 0.04, Monochromatic.


Enjoy.
